<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Safezone Counselling</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caveat:wght@600;700&family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,700;1,600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;
            color: #374151;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        .font-handwriting { font-family: 'Caveat', cursive; }
        .font-serif { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
        
        .text-brand-teal { color: #0f766e; }
        .text-brand-pink { color: #db2777; }
        .bg-brand-teal { background-color: #0f766e; }
        .bg-brand-teal:hover { background-color: #115e59; }
        .bg-brand-pink { background-color: #db2777; }
        .bg-brand-pink:hover { background-color: #be185d; }
        
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        input[type=range] { accent-color: #db2777; }

        .bg-certificate {
            background-color: #fff;
            background-image: radial-gradient(#0f766e 0.5px, transparent 0.5px), radial-gradient(#0f766e 0.5px, #fff 0.5px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex flex-col relative">

    <div class="h-2 w-full bg-brand-pink relative z-50"></div>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav id="main-nav" class="hidden bg-white shadow-sm container mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-sm font-bold tracking-wider text-teal-700 relative z-40">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6 mb-4 md:mb-0">
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="switchTab('beranda')" class="hover:text-pink-500 transition px-2 py-1">BERANDA</a>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="switchTab('asesmen')" class="hover:text-pink-500 transition px-2 py-1">ASESMEN</a>
            
            <div class="relative group">
                <button onclick="goToMateri()" class="hover:text-pink-500 transition px-2 py-1 flex items-center gap-1 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
                    MATERI
                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 md:left-0 md:translate-x-0 mt-2 w-56 bg-white border border-teal-100 rounded-xl shadow-2xl opacity-0 invisible group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:visible transition-all duration-300 z-[100] flex flex-col overflow-hidden">
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="bukaMateri('pemahaman-diri')" class="px-5 py-3 text-sm text-teal-700 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:text-brand-pink border-b border-gray-50 text-left transition-colors" id="nav-pemahaman-diri">1. Pemahaman Diri</a>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="bukaMateri('penerimaan-diri')" class="px-5 py-3 text-sm text-teal-700 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:text-brand-pink border-b border-gray-50 text-left transition-colors" id="nav-penerimaan-diri">2. Penerimaan Diri</a>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="bukaMateri('harga-diri')" class="px-5 py-3 text-sm text-teal-700 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:text-brand-pink border-b border-gray-50 text-left transition-colors" id="nav-harga-diri">3. Harga Diri</a>
                    <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="bukaMateri('diri-ideal')" class="px-5 py-3 text-sm text-teal-700 hover:bg-pink-50 hover:text-brand-pink text-left transition-colors" id="nav-diri-ideal">4. Diri Ideal</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="lihatSertifikat()" id="nav-sertifikat" class="hidden text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-600 transition px-2 py-1 flex items-center gap-1">🏆 SERTIFIKAT</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-2 md:mt-0">
            <div class="bg-teal-50 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-teal-100 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-xl">🎓</span>
                <span id="user-display-name" class="font-extrabold text-teal-800">Siswa</span>
            </div>
            <button onclick="logout()" class="text-xs text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500 underline">Keluar</button>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header id="main-header" class="hidden bg-white container mx-auto px-4 py-8 md:py-12 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 md:w-16 md:h-16 bg-teal-200 rounded-full border-2 border-gray-700 flex items-center justify-center relative shadow-[2px_2px_0px_0px_rgba(55,65,81,1)] shrink-0">
                <span class="text-xl md:text-2xl">🌱</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-brand-teal flex items-baseline flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
                <span>SAFEZONE</span>
                <span class="font-handwriting text-brand-pink text-4xl md:text-6xl font-normal lowercase relative top-1">counselling</span>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- LOADING SCREEN AWAL -->
    <div id="view-loading" class="hidden w-full flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-4">
        <svg class="animate-spin h-12 w-12 text-brand-teal mb-4" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle class="opacity-25" cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="4"></circle><path class="opacity-75" fill="currentColor" d="M4 12a8 8 0 018-8V0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12h4zm2 5.291A7.962 7.962 0 014 12H0c0 3.042 1.135 5.824 3 7.938l3-2.647z"></path></svg>
        <p class="text-teal-800 font-bold animate-pulse">Menghubungkan ke Sistem e-Safezone...</p>
    </div>

    <!-- HALAMAN 0: REGISTRASI SISWA -->
    <div id="view-register" class="hidden w-full flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-4">
        <div class="max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl border-4 border-teal-100 p-8 md:p-10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-pink-100 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-2xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-teal-100 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-2xl"></div>
            
            <div class="text-center relative z-10 mb-8">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-teal-50 rounded-full border-2 border-teal-200 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 shadow-sm">
                    <span class="text-4xl">👋</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal mb-2">Mulai Perjalananmu!</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Silakan daftar terlebih dahulu untuk menyimpan progres belajarmu di e-Safezone.</p>
            </div>

            <form id="form-register" onsubmit="window.prosesRegister(event)" class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-teal-800 mb-1">Nama Lengkap / Panggilan</label>
                    <input type="text" id="regNama" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-400 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white transition" placeholder="Misal: Aisyah Fitri" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-teal-800 mb-1">Alamat Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="regEmail" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-400 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white transition" placeholder="siswa@email.com" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-teal-800 mb-1">Kelas</label>
                    <input type="text" id="regKelas" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-400 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white transition" placeholder="Misal: VIII-A" required>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-sm font-bold text-teal-800 mb-1">Sekolah Asal</label>
                    <input type="text" id="regSekolah" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-teal-400 bg-gray-50 focus:bg-white transition" placeholder="Misal: MTsN 1 Pekanbaru" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-brand-pink text-white font-extrabold text-lg py-4 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:bg-pink-700 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1 mt-4">
                    Masuk ke e-Safezone &rarr;
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BAGIAN 1: HALAMAN BERANDA -->
    <div id="view-beranda" class="hidden w-full bg-white pb-12">
        <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-5xl">
            <div class="bg-teal-50/50 rounded-[2rem] p-6 md:p-12 border-2 border-teal-100 relative shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal lowercase mb-8 text-center lg:text-left break-words">
                    selamat datang <br class="hidden lg:block"><span class="font-handwriting text-brand-pink text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-wide capitalize" id="welcome-name">Sahabat!</span>
                </h2>
                
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-center lg:items-start">
                    <div class="flex-1 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-base md:text-lg text-justify md:text-left">
                        <p>
                            Ini bukan sekadar web biasa, lho! e-Safezone adalah layanan <em>cyber counselling</em> asyik yang siap jadi "zona aman" kamu buat bercerita, mengeksplorasi diri, dan bertumbuh menjadi versi terbaik dari dirimu melalui pengembangan <strong>Konsep Diri</strong>.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-pink-100 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-l-brand-pink relative">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-teal-800 mb-3 text-xl flex items-center gap-2"><span>🔍</span> Apa itu Konsep Diri?</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Secara sederhana, konsep diri adalah <strong>cara kamu memandang dan menilai dirimu sendiri</strong>. Ini mencakup bagaimana kamu melihat fisikmu, menyadari bakatmu, hingga menilai seberapa berharga dirimu di mata lingkunganmu.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-blue-50/50 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl border border-blue-100 shadow-sm relative">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3 text-xl flex items-center gap-2"><span>💡</span> Kenapa Konsep Diri yang Tinggi Itu Penting?</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Memiliki konsep diri yang positif membuat mentalmu jauh lebih tangguh. Kamu <strong>tidak akan mudah goyah atau depresi</strong> hanya karena kritikan atau standar <em>glowing</em> di internet.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-brand-teal p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-lg text-white mt-8 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 text-7xl opacity-10">🚀</div>
                            <h3 class="font-extrabold text-2xl mb-4 text-pink-300 font-handwriting tracking-wide relative z-10">Yuk, Mulai Perjalananmu!</h3>
                            <p class="mb-6 opacity-90 leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base relative z-10">Langkah pertama yang harus kamu lakukan adalah mengukur diri di ruang <strong>Asesmen</strong>.</p>
                            <button onclick="window.switchTab('asesmen')" class="bg-white text-teal-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-teal-50 transition shadow-lg w-full md:w-auto transform hover:-translate-y-1 text-lg relative z-20">
                                Ukur Konsep Diriku Sekarang &rarr;
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="shrink-0 relative w-[260px] h-[340px] md:w-80 md:h-[28rem] mx-auto mt-6 lg:mt-0 lg:sticky lg:top-8">
                        <img id="hero-image" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8101416/pexels-photo-8101416.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=800" alt="Siswa Muslimah" class="absolute inset-0 rounded-[2rem] shadow-lg border-4 border-white rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition duration-300 object-cover w-full h-full z-10">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- BAGIAN 2: HALAMAN DAFTAR MATERI -->
    <div id="view-daftar-materi" class="hidden w-full bg-white pb-12">
        <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex-1">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-pink-500 uppercase mb-2">Modul Pembelajaran</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal lowercase font-handwriting tracking-wide mb-4">Materi e-Safezone (Alur ARKA)</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-pink-400 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Pelajari materi di bawah ini dan selesaikan semua refleksinya untuk mendapatkan <strong>Centang Hijau ✅</strong>. Selesaikan semua modul untuk mendapatkan Sertifikat Penghargaanmu!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div id="banner-completion" class="hidden max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-pink-500 rounded-[2rem] p-8 text-white text-center shadow-xl transform transition hover:scale-[1.02]">
                <div class="text-6xl mb-4">🎉</div>
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2 uppercase tracking-widest">Luar Biasa, <span class="nama-siswa-dinamis">Sahabat</span>!</h3>
                <p class="text-lg mb-6 font-medium">Kamu telah menguasai dan menyelesaikan seluruh modul e-Safezone dengan sangat baik. Kami sangat bangga padamu!</p>
                <button onclick="window.lihatSertifikat()" class="bg-white text-brand-pink px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-extrabold shadow-md hover:bg-gray-50 transition text-lg animate-bounce">
                    Klaim Sertifikat Penghargaanmu 🏆
                </button>
            </div>

            <div id="materi-container" class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-8"></div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <!-- BAGIAN 3: HALAMAN BACA MATERI DETAIL -->
    <div id="view-baca-materi" class="hidden container mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex-1 max-w-4xl bg-white pb-12">
        <button onclick="window.goToMateri()" class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center text-teal-600 font-bold hover:text-teal-800 transition bg-teal-50 px-6 py-3 rounded-full shadow-sm relative z-20 cursor-pointer">
            &larr; Kembali ke Daftar Materi
        </button>
        
        <article class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
            <img id="detail-gambar" src="" alt="Cover Materi" class="w-full h-56 md:h-80 object-cover object-top">
            <div class="p-6 md:p-12">
                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-3">
                    <p id="detail-kategori" class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-pink-500 uppercase"></p>
                    <span id="badge-selesai-detail" class="hidden bg-green-500 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-bold shadow-sm">✅ SELESAI</span>
                </div>
                <h2 id="detail-judul" class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal mb-6 leading-tight break-words"></h2>
                
                <div class="bg-teal-50 p-6 rounded-2xl mb-8 border border-teal-100">
                    <h4 class="font-bold text-teal-800 mb-3 font-handwriting text-2xl">Alur Pembelajaran ARKA:</h4>
                    <ul class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 font-bold text-sm mt-4">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="bg-blue-500 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex justify-center items-center shrink-0">A</span> Aktivitas</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="bg-yellow-500 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex justify-center items-center shrink-0">R</span> Refleksi</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="bg-teal-500 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex justify-center items-center shrink-0">K</span> Konseptual</li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="bg-pink-500 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex justify-center items-center shrink-0">A</span> Aplikasi</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div id="detail-konten" class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg space-y-10"></div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>

    <!-- BAGIAN 4: HALAMAN ASESMEN (ANGKET) -->
    <div id="view-asesmen" class="hidden container mx-auto px-4 py-8 flex-1 max-w-4xl bg-white pb-12">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl border-4 border-teal-100 p-6 md:p-12 mb-12 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-teal-50 rounded-full opacity-50 blur-3xl"></div>
            
            <div class="text-center mb-10 relative z-10">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-pink-500 uppercase mb-2">Angket Kebutuhan Siswa</p>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal lowercase font-handwriting tracking-wide mb-4">Identifikasi Konsep Diri Islami</h2>
                <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-pink-400 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-justify md:text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    Assalamualaikum Warahmatullahi Wabarakatuh.<br>
                    <strong><span class="nama-siswa-dinamis">Sahabat</span></strong> yang hebat, Angket ini bertujuan untuk mengukur tingkat konsep diri yang kamu miliki saat ini. Jawablah sejujur-jujurnya sesuai dengan kata hatimu, kerahasiaanmu dijamin 100%.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div id="asesmen-form-section" class="relative z-10">
                <form id="form-angket" onsubmit="window.prosesAngket(event)">
                    <div class="bg-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 border border-teal-100 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-xs text-teal-600 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Identitas Tersimpan</p>
                            <p class="font-extrabold text-teal-900 text-lg"><span class="nama-siswa-dinamis">Siswa</span> (<span id="kelas-siswa-display">Kelas</span>)</p>
                            <p class="text-sm text-teal-700" id="sekolah-siswa-display">Sekolah</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm text-2xl">📝</div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6 px-2">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-700">Petunjuk Pengisian:</p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Pilih salah satu jawaban yang paling sesuai dengan kondisimu saat ini.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- WADAH PERTANYAAN ANGKET -->
                    <div id="angket-form-container"></div>

                    <div class="text-center mt-10 bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-gray-200">
                        <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium mb-4">Sudah yakin dengan semua jawabanmu?</p>
                        <button type="submit" class="bg-brand-pink text-white font-bold text-lg px-12 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-pink-700 transition shadow-lg transform hover:-translate-y-1 w-full md:w-auto relative z-20 cursor-pointer">
                            Kirim & Lihat Hasil Analisis
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div id="hasil-asesmen" class="hidden relative z-10">
                <div class="bg-teal-50/50 rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-10 border-2 border-teal-200 text-center">
                    <div class="inline-block bg-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-md mb-4 border border-teal-100">
                        <span class="text-5xl">✨</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-teal-800 mb-2">Hasil Analisis Konsep Diri</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8" id="pesan-terima-kasih">Terima kasih telah mengisi angket dengan jujur.</p>

                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 mb-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">
                        <p id="skor-total" class="text-xl mb-2"></p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">Semakin tinggi kategorimu, semakin positif pemahaman konsep diri islami yang kamu miliki.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-pink-100 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto border-t-4 border-t-brand-pink text-left relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute -right-4 -top-4 text-6xl opacity-10">🎯</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-2 text-center relative z-10">Fokus Pengembangan Utama:</h4>
                        <p class="text-center text-3xl font-handwriting text-brand-pink mb-4 relative z-10" id="dimensi-terendah"></p>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 text-center relative z-10">Dimensi ini mencatat persentase pemahaman paling rendah. Ini adalah area pertama yang perlu kita perkuat bersama.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-left max-w-lg mx-auto bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm mb-8">
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-700 mb-4 text-center">Rincian Persentase Per Dimensi</h4>
                        <div id="detail-dimensi" class="space-y-4"></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-brand-teal text-white rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 max-w-lg mx-auto shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4 text-7xl opacity-10 font-handwriting">Yuk!</div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-3 relative z-10 text-pink-300">Langkah Selanjutnya</h4>
                        <p class="font-medium text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed relative z-10 mb-6 opacity-90 text-left">
                            Silakan pelajari <strong>Modul Materi</strong> (terutama fokus pada dimensimu yang terendah) dan selesaikan semua refleksinya ya!
                        </p>
                        <button type="button" onclick="window.goToMateri()" class="bg-white text-teal-800 px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-teal-50 transition shadow-md w-full relative z-20 cursor-pointer transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                            Buka Daftar Modul Materi &rarr;
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <button type="button" onclick="window.ulangAsesmen()" class="mt-8 bg-transparent text-gray-400 px-6 py-2 rounded-full text-sm hover:text-gray-600 transition underline">
                        Isi Ulang Angket
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
